==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lene
<hw>Lene</hw> <pr>(l⟦emac⟧n)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Lend</er>.]</ety> <def>To lend; to grant; to permit.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
